<div>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-left">
      <h4>
        <span class="dollar-logo">
          <%= image_tag "logo00.png", alt: "Logo" %>
        </span>
        CostShare
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div class="navbar-center">
      <%= link_to "Login", login_path, class: "nav-btn" %>
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path, class: "nav-btn" %>
    </div>
    <div class="navbar-right">
      <%= link_to "Home" %>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- main container -->
  <div class="main-container">
    <!-- row one -->
    <div class="row">
      <div style="padding-bottom: 10px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 20px;">Split Expenses Effortlessly with Friends</h3>
        <p style="text-align: center;">CostShare makes it simple to track shared expenses, settle debts, and maintain financial harmony in your social circle.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- 3 cards -->
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">
            <i class="fas fa-receipt"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Track Group Expense</h4>
            <p>Easily record and categorize expenses shared with roomates, friends, or travel companies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">
            <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Smart Debt calculation</h4>
            <p>Our algorithm optimizes who pays whom, minimizing the number of transactions needed to settle up.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bell"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Payment Reminders</h4>
            <p>Send gentle reminders to friends who owe you money without the awkward conversations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- row two -->
    <div class="row-with-image">
      <div class="img-container">
        <%= image_tag "image03.jpg", alt: "Home Page Image", class: "home-page-image" %>
      </div>
      <div class="image-content">
        <h3>Simplify Group Finances</h3>
        <p>Whether you're sharing an apartment, planing a vacation, or just going out for dinner, ShareCost helps you keep track of who paid for what and who owne whom.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>✅ Create multiple groups for different sharing scenarios</li>
          <li>✅ Integrate with payment platforms for instant settlements</li>
          <li>✅ Track individual and group expenses in one place</li>
          <li>✅ Split bills evenly or by custom percentages</li>
          <li>✅ Send automatic reminders to settle up</li>
          <li>✅ View detailed balance summaries for each group</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- row three -->
    <div class="row">
      <h3>How It Works</h3>
      <div class="cards-without_gap">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">1</div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Create a Group</h4>
            <p>Add friends to your expense-sharing group</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">2</div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Log Expenses</h4>
            <p>Record who paid and how to split the cost</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">3</div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Track Balances</h4>
            <p>See how ownes what at a glance</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">4</div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Settle Up</h4>
            <p>Pay or receive money to clear debts</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- row four -->
    <div class="row">
      <div>
        <h3>Ready to simplify your shared expenses?</h3>
        <div class="one-row-text">
          <div></div>
          <div class="cta-text">Get Start for Free   </div>
          <div style="text-align: end; color: green;">Learn More</div>
        </div>
        <p style="text-align: end;">Add expenses in any currency with automatic conversion</p>
        <h3>What Our Users Say</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card feedback-card">
          <div class="user-feedback">
            <div class="icon-name">EC</div>
            <div class="name-and-rate">
              <p>Emily Chen</p>
              <p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>"ShareCost saved our friendship during our Europ trip! No more awkward money converstion or trying to remember who paid for what."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feedback-card">
          <div class="user-feedback">
            <div class="icon-name">MJ</div>
            <div class="name-and-rate">
              <p>Marcus Johnson</p>
              <p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>"As roomates, we use this app daily. The expense tracking is intuitive and the debt calculation is spot on. Highly recommend!"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feedback-card">
          <div class="user-feedback">
            <div class="icon-name">SR</div>
            <div class="name-and-rate">
              <p>Sofia Rodriguez</p>
              <p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>"I organize group dinners weekly, and this app has been a game-changer. The ability to split bills unevenly is exactly what we needed."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* Navbar */
  body, html {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f3f3f3;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #1d917a;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      color: white;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      z-index: 1000;
  }
  .navbar h4 {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 0;
  }
  .navbar .dollar-logo img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      margin-right: 8px;
  }
  .nav-btn {
      background: white;
      color: #1d917a;
      border: none;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-left: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-btn:hover {
      background-color: #0ca694;
      color: white;
  }
  .navbar-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
  }
  .navbar-right a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
  }

  .main-container {
    padding-top: 100px;
    padding-bottom: 90px;
    padding-left: 60px;
    padding-right: 60px;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .main-container h3, .main-container h4 {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cards, .cards-without_gap {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 250px;
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .feedback-card {
    align-items: start;
  }
  /* Icon styles */

  .icon, .icon-name {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #1d917a;
  background-color: rgba(29, 145, 122, 0.1); /* light green transparent */
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.icon-name {
  font-size: 16px;
  width: 38px;
  height: 38px;
}

.user-feedback {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.name-and-rate {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.name-and-rate p {
  margin: 2px 0;
  font-size: 14px;
}

  /* Card Content */
  .card-content h4 {
    margin: 0;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .card-content p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
  }

  .image-content ul li {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 4px;
  }


  /* Headings */
  h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #1d917a;
  }
  /* Rows */
  .row {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .one-row-text {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    padding-top: 10px;
  }
  .one-row-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .cta-text {
    background-color: #1d917a;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
  }

  .cta-text:hover {
  background-color: #0c7f68;   
}

   /* image */
  .row-with-image {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .row-with-image img {
    width: 460px;
  }

  /* Home image */
  .home-page-image {
    max-width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 1px 1px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  /* Responsive Layout */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .navbar {
          padding: 10px;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .navbar-center, .navbar-right {
          align-items: center;
          display: flex;
      }
      h3 {
          font-size: 16px;
      }
      .row-with-image {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .main-container {
        padding-top: 80px;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
        padding-left: 40px;
        padding-right: 40px;
      }
      .navbar {
          padding: 8px 12px;
      }
      .navbar h4 {
          font-size: 14px;
      }
      .navbar .dollar-logo img {
          width: 22px;
          height: 22px;
          margin-right: 5px;
      }
      .nav-btn {
          padding: 4px 8px;
          font-size: 12px;
          margin-left: 4px;
      }
      .navbar-right {
          gap: 6px;
      }

  }
</style>
